Spring Bank Plc., nke a na-akpọkwa Spring Bank, bụ ụlọ akụ azụmahịa na Naijiria
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ụlọ akụ azụmahịa iri abụọ na isii (26) nke Central Bank of Nigeria nyere ikike, onye na-ahụ maka ụlọ akụ nke mba ahụ n'oge ahụ.
Spring Bank bụ nnukwu onye na-enye ọrụ ego na Naịjirịa

As of June 2010[update] 2010[update], e mere atụmatụ na ngụkọta akụ ụlọ akụ ahụ dị ihe dị ka US $1.31 billion (NGN: 201.3 billion). E depụtara ngwaahịa nke Spring Bank na Naịjirịa Stock Exchange, ebe ọ na-ere ahịa n'okpuru akara: SPRINGBANK.
E guzobere Spring Bank na Disemba 2005 site na njikọta nke ụlọ ọrụ ego Naijiria isii, ya bụ:
N'oge e guzobere ya, Spring Bank nwere isi obodo nke ihe dịka US$224 million (NGN: 34.5 billion) na ngụkọta akụ e mere atụmatụ na ihe dịka US$988 million (NG N:152 billion).

N'afọ 2009, na-agbaso nyocha ụlọ ọrụ niile nke ụlọ akụ azụmahịa niile dị na mba ahụ, Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN), onye na-achịkwa ụlọ akụ na mba ahụ، chọtara ụlọ akụ azụmaahịa itoolu na-enweghị isi na nke a na-achịchaghị nke ọma
Spring Bank bụ otu n'ime ụlọ akụ nwere nsogbu
CBN batara site na itinye isi obodo ọhụrụ iji nọgide na-akwụ ụgwọ ma họpụta njikwa ọhụrụ
N'abalị ise n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2011, CBN wepụrụ ikike ụlọ akụ nke Spring Bank.
E guzobere ụlọ akụ Enterprise Bank n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2011 site n'iweghara akụ na ụfọdụ ụgwọ nke ụlọ akụ Spring Bank, nke a kagbuola ikike ụlọ akụ azụmahịa ya
E nyere EBL ikike ụlọ akụ azụmahịa na 5 Ọgọst 2011
Ka ọ na-erule Jenụwarị 2012, akụ nke Enterprise Bank Limited bụ 100% nke Asset Management Company of Nigeria (AMCON), otu aka nke Gọọmentị Federal nke Nigeria
N'ọnwa Julaị n'afọ 2012, Ụlọikpe Kasị Elu nke Naịjirịa, na Lagos nyere iwu ka a kwụsị ọrụ nke Spring Bank Plc, ebe ọ bụ na a kagbuola ikikere ya.
Mgbe Central Bank of Nigeria batara n'ọrụ na 2009, a họpụtara Bernadina Sola Ayodele dịka onye isi nchịkwa na onye isi nchịk.
